column5: 2066 threw counter some issues have risen with 26 year old counter but we are making the best of it water has taken a sudden tempature drop it is now 4.6 degrees
i take it this is a poor fish count..
So far, but the weather hasnt played in the fishes favour, but certainly played in the fishermans favour, warmer temps will see the count rise, thanx Jase for the update
Water temp today.  1c. That is crazy for this time of year. Pray for warm weather or the slaughter will be on
It's looking better, +8 tomorrow and double digits with sun Saturday and Sunday.  Rich.
Cool!  26 year old counter.  Fresh out of college probably.  Should know his numbers, shouldn't be problems with the count.
Bunk, pretty sure its an automated counter lol , i've been thinking of putting one in our river but its hard to find an accurate one.  Joseph
It doesn't need to be accurate, you can just make up numbers to suit your needs  S.
Maybe the counter is a 26 yr old female, she hoists the fish and the men count, everytime she bends down to net some more, problems arise with the counts.
